                 "Unsolicited `offer` frames can create local operator notifications with host-owned `inac.invitation.accept` / `inac.invitation.reject` actions"
                 "Accept is idempotent for already accepted offers, receiver-issued invitation passport TTL is configurable, and active pending offers are capped per remote node"
                 "Accepted invitations create a local INAC contact projection by default; the contact is not authority"
